settings.title:
First things first.
THIS is Saalt Period Underwear.

settings.text_content: Reusable, absorbent, leakproof underwear that keeps you dry and confident. It absorbs periods, bladder leaks, and more, and completely replaces disposable pads or liners.

settings.title: And this is how it works

settings.text_content: Our patent-pending gusset technology instantly wicks away wetness to keep you feeling dry while absorbing up to 3 pads worth of flow. Ta-da!

settings.title: What makes Saalt better? Glad you asked.

settings.text_content: As a B Corp, we like to keep it clean for both you and the planet. That means we don’t treat our period underwear with harmful PFAS, and we source all of our fabrics sustainably.

settings.title: We're here to get you to period bliss.

settings.text_content: If you’re not happy with your period underwear or other Saalt products, we’ll send you a replacement you’ll love or your money back per our Period Bliss Guarantee.

settings.title:
Which absorbency do you need?
Let’s break it down.

settings.text_content: Saalt period underwear comes in 4 levels of absorbency for different needs.
Easy peasy. Take good care of Saalt Wear and it will take great care of you.
Do not use fabric softener or bleach to protect the tech | Do not iron

settings.title: SEAMLESS
settings.text_content: Made with ultra-durable LYCRA®️ XTRA LIFE™️ fiber which resists fit loss and provides you with the confidence that your garment will last after repeated wash and wear.

settings.title: COMFORT
settings.text_content: Made from soft-stretch TENCEL™️ Modal, aka dreamy soft fabric made from sustainably regenerated cellulose fiber that comes from renewable beech wood.

settings.title: LACE & MESH
settings.text_content: Each pair is made with an average of 3 post-consumer recycled water bottles to help clean up landfill and ocean-bound plastic.

settings.title: Cotton
settings.text_content:
Made of soft and breathable biodegradable natural cotton that is Standard 100 OEKO-TEX®️ Certified.
This is a 3rd party certification that our product is free from a wide list of harmful chemicals.
